                    <span>I would recomend this book to anyone wanting to create a fps. This book has helped me put my ideas together and point me in the right direction for creating my own engine and game. This book is definatly worth every penny.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Top Notch Code</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
